
Bomba Client
============


Development Environment
-----------------------

The client is implemented in the C++ programming language using, CMake as a
build, and Git as a version control systems. They are required prerequisites.

The game depends on following tools and libraries
  * Irrlicht 3D Game Engine 
  * Google Protocol Buffers

For Ubuntu Linux the standard repositories does contain required packages
  $ sudo apt-get install libirrlicht-dev libprotobuf-dev protobuf-compiler


Build
-----

Use CMake and Make in order to build the source code
  $ cd build && cmake . && make

The binaries will end-up in bin

